    <div class="res-row"><div class="res-label">ARB stiffness</div><div class="res-val empty" id="arb-f-res">—</div><div class="res-val empty" id="arb-r-res">—</div></div>
    <p class="note">
      <b>Guide (AWD):</b> Start at 1 front / 65 rear (max rear). If oversteer → reduce rear or increase front. The closer the values are to each other, the more understeer.<br>
      <b>RWD:</b> Front lower than rear. Softer front = more oversteer. Softer rear = more understeer.<br>
      After changing ARBs, compensate with springs in opposite direction.
